.TP
.B \fB\-firrefutable\-tuples\fP
Make tuple pattern matching irrefutable
.TP
.B \fB\-fpackage\-trust\fP
Enable Safe Haskell trusted package requirement for trustworthy modules.
.TP
.B \fB\-ftype\-function\-depth=⟨n⟩\fP
